{"tid":1368228,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[教學] 你入元朗我帶路! 元朗教學","createTime":"2019-07-26T12:26:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T16:14:51.000Z","uid":117529,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"caeb105ad39629d377c46d751f02c676f290b29c","tid":1368228,"uid":117529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:26:18.000Z","msg":"Hello 又係我元朗人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見大家呢幾日對元朗咁有興趣，身為土生土長元朗人，一定要比大家知道元朗有咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.地理分佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.何為大馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.著名地標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.交通路線<br />\n5.諗到再講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.</span></span> 元朗既地理分佈，以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大馬路</span></span>為中心，向四周散射出去，但如果要比喻，我會形容為 <strong>三文治</strong><br />\n                                                          <br />\n                                    <div style=\"text-align: center;\">鄉<br />\n                                    村<br />\n (往天水圍屯門) 西                        大馬路                            東 (往錦田上水九龍)<br />\n                                    村<br />\n                                    鄉</div><br />\n<br />\n咁講會有少少誇張，但好認真咁講，當你離開大馬路，去到其他橫街馬路，第一次入元朗，真係會唔識路架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />四通八達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我建議，唔太識路既朋友，除非有相熟朋友帶路啦，如果唔係盡量唔好離開大馬路範圍。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然我知如果有咁多朋友想入黎參觀元朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />肯定路都無得行，如果真係要深入既，請記得返去既路線。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.1 街道<br />\n有幾條街同地方大家都要認識下，身為元朗人唔會唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有錯歡迎指出<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又新街 (串燒街 / 食街)</span></span><br />\n呢到真係有好多野食架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 例如有串燒，燒賣，珍珠奶茶，西式日式，牛排刺身，雞蛋仔，食粥食飯食狗仔粉，狗糧都有得賣添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又新街上面最少都有三間便利店，7仔OK任君選擇。<br />\n要知道又新街都幾長下，可以一直通去馬會投注處，Physical，銀湖芬蘭浴室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但又新街都連接住一部分舊區，有時都有南亞朋友，而且有多條橫街出去，夠鐘就要睇時間走啦，<strong>不宜久留</strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">教育路</span></span><br />\n講到教育路，不得不提就係千色 (圖片取自google map)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YWWYDvM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYWWYDvM.png&h=38e723a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>黑色箭嘴 : 通往大棠</strong><br />\n<strong>紅色箭嘴 : 真，教育路</strong><br />\n呢條街都有好多野食架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有好多唔同既小鋪頭，都有雞蛋仔，奶茶etc，大家可以入去食下放題，真日式放題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要休息下，仲有M記添，有廁所，24小時開放架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LTn5iwn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLTn5iwn.jpg&h=13cee484&s={SIZE}\" />(取自盡在元朗FB)<br />\n當你見到以上景色，加埋間 M記，就代表你無去錯地方啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n背向千色，一直向前行，就會去到 <strong>元朗警察已婚宿舍</strong>，<strong>元朗警署 </strong>，<strong>元朗大球場</strong>，<strong>水邊圍遊樂場</strong>，再行多幾步，就係<strong>元朗劇院</strong>，<strong>元朗游泳池</strong><br />\n都係驚大家唔識路，就唔好行太遠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2.何為大馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n朋友入到黎，如果驚唔記得路，請記住<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大馬路 = 輕鐵路軌</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大馬路起點</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JmTzWpU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJmTzWpU.png&h=672fe3ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大馬路終點</span> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6GYcH8p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6GYcH8p.png&h=67f9009d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n再向直行，就唔係大馬路架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好去錯地方啊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">著名地標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n元朗咁大，咁多鋪頭，驚大家行到亂，點都要認下路認下地標既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">榮華</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TwjWqsP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTwjWqsP.png&h=c7602c22&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n元朗自設既大工場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見到榮華就識路啦<br />\n向東走，就係西鐵站啦，都可以去到雞地，如果轉入日新街，阜財街，大棠路，就可以入到又新街，千色廣場，教育路，光華廣場，合益街市，華星冰室，好到底麵家，入去元朗新街仲可以買下生果添<br />\n<br />\n講住咁多先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為實在太多太多，不能盡錄，等等再同大家講下交通，重要位置等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後一定要補多句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>我愛元朗，我愛香港</strong></span>"},{"pid":"28982fd0441da21b6f33336762aef0702632475a","tid":1368228,"uid":117529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:27:04.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"a8ca06bb8f2a82643502e385d8070e459ca5141e","tid":1368228,"uid":117529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:27:27.000Z","msg":"推啊X2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b35bbcf69bc898aca76768eaf84e1498bfd0914c","tid":1368228,"uid":117529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:27:37.000Z","msg":"推啊X3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6781e3f45986ff06f9747b33ab2261ed82f3d5d","tid":1368228,"uid":117529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:28:28.000Z","msg":"推啊X2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd1ab2c1351a0e778039dc61352c3e772143b96b","tid":1368228,"uid":117529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:28:45.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ab312d490157355db8543b382f3656e9d978ec","tid":1368228,"uid":117529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:28:55.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9102529a5762dacbcfd752b227374988365c922c","tid":1368228,"uid":36761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m64n5cK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm64n5cK.jpg&h=434be3bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc940b604225f28d6e6a8fb5883b30a3a3f3827c","tid":1368228,"uid":72477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:33:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EVStgFV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEVStgFV.png&h=4cb2fbbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n借圖一轉"},{"pid":"67838989d0d93edad5ed20b9113685f7a093db03","tid":1368228,"uid":117529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:50:27.000Z","msg":"推啊屌，得咁少人推?"},{"pid":"e6254b84913eaaa4fcb43d3df0e0ad1d132fe4ea","tid":1368228,"uid":233385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:53:44.000Z","msg":"巴打好有心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日一齊加油！"},{"pid":"f0510e2db1d8f0b02bc844b18b5bb68b91e69edb","tid":1368228,"uid":117529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:54:22.000Z","msg":"推啊屌"},{"pid":"d21d8b841653f0055c6c1444d653ad8ce79461f9","tid":1368228,"uid":117529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:54:56.000Z","msg":"仲講張建宗托咩，你識點行未啊"},{"pid":"5532b73b0566ed51a8c879cac2d1b0affb9ce0bd","tid":1368228,"uid":117529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:55:17.000Z","msg":"唔想見到你地係元朗比人圍住屌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f770593ddcb044612026daedb9606f43fdf0b6","tid":1368228,"uid":117529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:55:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee9da565840488265793e62de53c4f8bdb540beb","tid":1368228,"uid":117529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:57:25.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"ebfa4fd8c3c95d8dc5ce4063e8c975355dd0416e","tid":1368228,"uid":117529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:57:41.000Z","msg":"唉求下你地入黎睇啦，打左我兩個鐘"},{"pid":"2814629e604b070ee472852c9b17e8e61f87952a","tid":1368228,"uid":117529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:00:29.000Z","msg":"入黎啦好嗎"},{"pid":"0ddc50de418e69b9b00da5300713ec64cf59bc01","tid":1368228,"uid":117529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:00:39.000Z","msg":"唉好傷心"},{"pid":"41e5697b3aafd7df849fdd6eb8e2a9580b5beaca","tid":1368228,"uid":117529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:02:01.000Z","msg":"入黎睇下啦求下你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa055752e1c2ccc741b3a3987d7dd7ad0603a0a5","tid":1368228,"uid":117529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:02:11.000Z","msg":"你真係識曬路啦咩"},{"pid":"161a397afe1ed232ad2a3b321e04b557891b1ac2","tid":1368228,"uid":117529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:06:35.000Z","msg":"唉無心機推"},{"pid":"b9f1bbd7728ecbdddda6cb300552b774ac6ed7ad","tid":1368228,"uid":17878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:11:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b244311fbf1e32266818a07be8a012dcb06924b8","tid":1368228,"uid":17878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:13:26.000Z","msg":"第3 4 5 6呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲人可能聽日就會見到你個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67a51af5b099020247573c60e02ca545780b9ce","tid":1368228,"uid":287382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:13:27.000Z","msg":"（多圖入！）元朗小肥絲帶你遊元朗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1368918\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1368918</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有咩好過睇一個指南，係睇兩個呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}